","msg":"講咁多嘢，但都係要等到國際形勢配合、外來政權內部瓦解，先至會有轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無可能追求畫面靚，同埋為做而做而不停咁樣去作肢體衝突，可能大家死去嘅日子都唔會見到黑暗完結嘅一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20200210/s00022/1581261045118/%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E8%98%87%E5%85%B1%E4%B8%8B%E5%A0%B4%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%97%8E-%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E6%B4%9B%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20200210%2Fs00022%2F1581261045118%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%2598%2587%25E5%2585%25B1%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%2597%258E-%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%2596%2587-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25B4%259B%25EF%25BC%2589&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10GINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=ea0e79a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20200210%2Fs00022%2F1581261045118%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%2598%2587%25E5%2585%25B1%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%2597%258E-%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%2596%2587-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25B4%259B%25EF%25BC%2589&h=a5c1ac4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20200210/s00022/1581261045118/%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E8%98%87%E5%85%B1%E4%B8%8B%E5%A0%B4%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%97%8E-%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E6%B4%9B%EF%BC%89</a><br />\n高登仔外父－陳家洛：中共和蘇共下場會不同嗎？"},{"pid":"041e211c3bba589bcbb164b69d477170f99a80fd","tid":1975363,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4625c21ede8278e8c1acdfe21f408f1f1604493","tid":1975363,"uid":40537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"762a331f4e7e8282b34bde6b1848f097d06689db","tid":1975363,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6858f2f397ae8e5b20d1d0261ba8c2bdae82fc1","tid":1975363,"uid":75444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2436501d44ac2da370fca02f8737eed01ca286e2","tid":1975363,"uid":75444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"做自己可以做到嘅嘢"},{"pid":"cbfc98264660274119a2c828d8001cfef4044a60","tid":1975363,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"小學雞政治頭腦<br />\n非我即敵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係呀伍公子，講撚緊你"},{"pid":"285ffda1aab65d929861b6e95538059bb81e64f0","tid":1975363,"uid":330728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb6ae721ea738adabdc61941bbba7b1608838d43","tid":1975363,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"場仗好難贏，香港人要贏就要進步變得更聰明。<br />\n避免自己人分化之餘亦要<span style=\"color: red;\">避免陷入對家所形造既分化氛圍</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同路未必同道，亦不必同道。只要向著同一個方向，沒有最好的做法，只有最多的方法。<br />\n每個人專注做番自己做緊既野，做番自己認為最可行既野，先可以將勝算推到最大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>波蘭學生抗爭三途</ins></strong><br />\n八十年代初波蘭共黨政府實行軍法統治，打壓言論自由，大學生抗爭兵分三路:一，地下文宣派，二，勇武行動派，三，綠色和平派。三派各有各做，必要時互相合作，直到八九六四後，蘇聯爆炸，波共倒台。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>地下文宣派</strong><br />\n七十年代的波蘭學生尚多少相信社會主義會帶來繁榮安定，八十年代則對波共完全無期望。其時，波蘭獨立學生聯會(Niezależne Zrzeszenie Student&oacute;w/NZS /獨聯)要求釋放政治犯、學術自由、教育資源公平分配，與波共老人統治有世代之爭，與波蘭團結工會同醒同氣，常罷課遊行。一九八一年十二月波共實施軍法統治，宣布獨聯為非法組織。獨聯與波蘭團結工會結盟，聯合中學生組織，轉入地下工作，辦民間電台，出地下雜誌，暗中派傳單。獨聯遭禁後，多得不少良心教授及天主教教區庇護，學生計劃周詳，狡免三窟，然仍有多人被捕，動轍判監兩年之久，然而義士前仆後繼，誓不低頭。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>勇武行動派</strong><br />\n一九八一年十一月，宣布軍法統治後數日，勇武團結力量（Solidarność Walcząca）發起大遊行，有二千位學生參加，此後不時以汽油彈與黑警對抗。八二年十一月，波共宣布團結工會為非法組織後，勇武團結力量的學生更與黑警巷戰。一九八三年，無政府主義學生組織，另類社會運動 (Społeczeństwa Alternatywnego /RSA)於格旦斯克成立，不單反共，而且認為波蘭團結工會路線太溫和。一九八五年五月一號勞動節，RSA發起反官方大遊行，衝破防暴警察防線，佔領建制派論壇，火併黑警，喋血街頭。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>綠色和平派</strong><br />\n自由和平運動 (Wolność i Pok&oacute;j /WiP):，以環保人權、和平反戰議題，和理非非，公開活動，爭取國際支持。此外，波蘭JAROCIN每年五月三號舉行新生代樂與怒音樂節，音樂節本身非政治，成千上萬青年，包括抗爭份子，湧到該市，聽另類音樂，抗衡官方洗腦文化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B8%89%E9%80%94/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2580%2594%2F&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10GINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=cc056db9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2580%2594%2F&h=641c513d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B8%89%E9%80%94/</a></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:43:48.000Z","msg":"樓主也可以找找80年代未，韓國學生運動<br />\n金斗煥運動"},{"pid":"22c4ea6df9e2af8a3516d57817d0e1d27cd40262","tid":1975363,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd0293e666d96fe60bfe52f46836f7c2f47eb3e","tid":1975363,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkg